flowRoot.flowPara: Figure Graph-Genome-Generation. Graph representation (left) and unique variants (right) produced by [name of step]. From the global multiple sequence alignment, all unique paths through the graph genome are enumerated and written to final output file (in this case, a VCF file). In this example, the reference genome (grey) serves as a scaffold to which all contigs (blue, green, and orange) are aligned. Reading from
